title: FF Ronnie Massey - UnSpoken: A Val and Irulan Short (Darklife Sa
description:
Prequel to Crimson Dawn (Darklife Saga)

Summary:

What happens when a headstrong vampire and a faerie princess decide to live together as roommates...fireworks! Check out the latest installment in the Darklife Shorts, prequels to my upcoming novel Crimson Dawn.

For two years pureblood vampire, Valeria Trumaine and Sidhe princess, Irulan Nightingale, have lived together as roommates. Life long friends; the two thought that nothing could come between them, but they were wrong.

When emotions that Irulan has avoided acknowledging, refuse to remain hidden any longer, her frustration with untold secrets and old grievances drive her to an 'open-mouth-insert-foot' moment with Valeria; driving the two apart.

But when two roommates fall out, it's usually not a life or death situation...unless both of you are super powered Extras.
